javamoon.construct.binary
Class ClassLoader

java.lang.Object
  javamoon.construct.binary.ClassLoader

public class ClassLoader
extends java.lang.Object

A class loader loads the list of class files, using a class constructor to add elements to the current model.

Since:
JavaMoon-2.0.1
Author:
Raúl Marticorena
